box;\">3. <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">프로그램 활동 기간</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> : 2026. 6. 20.(토) ~ 7. 18.(토</span>) (약 4주간)</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 38.5pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\">4. 지원자격</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\">가. 2026-1학기 ‘학부’ 재학생으로서, 학년 및 전공 제한 없음</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">    ※ 휴학생·수료생 및 정규 8학기 초과생은 버디교류활동은 가능하나</span>, 장학금 수혜 불가</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11.25pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;'><span style=\"box-