>◆</span></span><span style='font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 11pt;'><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">표시된 일자에 문화체험 활동 진행</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11.25pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\">5. 신청기간 및 방법</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">가. 신청기간 : </span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:verdana;font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:11.0pt;\">2026. 5. 8.(</span><span style=\"font-family:verdana;mso-fareast-font-family:verdana;font-size:11.0pt;\">금</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:verdana;font-family:Verdana;mso-ascii-font-family:Verdana;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-size:11.0pt;\">) ~ 5. 21.(</span><span style=\"font-family:verdana;mso-fareast-font-family:verdana;font-size:11.0pt;\">목</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:verdana;font-family: